{"tid":2137688,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大媽無視限聚令中環碼頭演唱 認罪罰款三千元","createTime":"2020-08-03T06:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T06:14:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dba7ae915ab6ed2717c020796192c030d25cb486","tid":2137688,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:14:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200803/BHZ5AWLXNW2HJDGBM3R3CAVSJQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200803%2FBHZ5AWLXNW2HJDGBM3R3CAVSJQ%2F&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2FwV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=b7e9d228\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200803%2FBHZ5AWLXNW2HJDGBM3R3CAVSJQ%2F&h=588f5f3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200803/BHZ5AWLXNW2HJDGBM3R3CAVSJQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n本港武漢肺炎疫情自年初開始持續失控，惟多名在中環碼頭表演歌唱的大媽今年4月疑無視限聚令，在碼頭附近放置擴音器及凳仔作表演，吸引途人駐足觀看，遭女警放蛇斷正。其中一名大媽今在東區裁判法院承認一項組織受禁羣組聚集傳票罪。裁判官斥現場有凳有音響，自然有人聚集，違反公眾安全；並謂組織者嚴重過參與者，判被告罰款3,000元。"}]}